              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31418413/" class="">《政治思考：一些永久性问题》摘抄</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/vankov/" class=" " title="Hu">Hu</a>
                (坏人追求帕累托 好人免费被搭车)
              
